'''''Minelayer''''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Beta-class ETR-3 escort transport|''Beta''-class ETR-3 escort transport]] equipped with one or more [[Minelayer (weapon system)|minelayers]]. It was tasked with laying a [[Space mine/Legends|mine]] field around [[Comm Center]], and was presumably destroyed by either the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] pilots who attacked that station or the [[Azzameen family]], who hacked into the base's systems.

